text: @RexChapman Same with my daughter Irvine, CA.  All the symptoms, very sick, 2 tests each took 8-10 days for results that were FALSE NEGATIVE! Doctor said tests are terrible, she definately has COVID19 (all other things ruled out) and they are going to test her next for antibodies. Travesty
